com.here.android.mpa.routing

Enum Maneuver.Icon

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Maneuver.Icon>
      • com.here.android.mpa.routing.Maneuver.Icon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Maneuver.Icon>
    Enclosing class:
    Maneuver

    public static enum Maneuver.Icon
extends java.lang.Enum<Maneuver.Icon>
    Represents values describing types of Maneuver icons.

    Note that this enum is only provided as a convenience to easily retrieve the maneuver instruction. You must provide your own icon images and implement your own icon-drawing code.
